{"tid":1913701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屈人係藍絲具有殺傷力","createTime":"2020-03-07T04:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T05:13:02.000Z","uid":276872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e720b7fee4077bfecc165b873874af7c32a84c","tid":1913701,"uid":276872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"依家係咪太得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？咁鍾意屈自己唔鍾意/討厭嘅名人係藍絲，坦白講屈人係藍絲真係可以收人皮，咁大殺傷力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。以下係屈藍手段：<br />\n① 運動初期無乜表態<br />\n② 發表意見時非直接，無講口號<br />\n③ 運動發生前與藍絲接觸(E.g於2019年1至5月與<span style=\"color: blue;\">朋友</span>食飯/訪問/約會)<br />\n④ 運動時去旅行(6-8月屈得最勁)<br />\n④ <span style=\"color: red;\">最撚離譜</span>：內部員工爆料<br />\n<br />\n屈人班友對被屈者係呢埸嘅付出就見唔到，例如<span style=\"color: red;\">遊行/去理大中大捐物資救人</span>，反而將呢啲①-④就無限放大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。究竟係咪門檻高咗依家食咗TG先稱得上係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？如果真係乜都無做過先當佢係藍。<br />\n<br />\n最後，屈人係藍絲真係具有殺傷力，可以攻擊下自己討厭對象。"},{"pid":"2f1741692959669e478c74c76c869970d967b177","tid":1913701,"uid":276872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:21:08.000Z","msg":"屈人係藍嘅人同荷蘭叻一樣，對於人哋付出表示：&ldquo;我睇唔到，聽唔到&rdquo;"},{"pid":"b6931bfb94a2aa22b5a75dc4fdf967a8df0eab98","tid":1913701,"uid":276872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:21:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cacad3f6dcf22ae8ff5dad9c6723bf7e980ca7ab","tid":1913701,"uid":276872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bc6cccdc3fffe495a2c83f8903c01a4f2022a1d","tid":1913701,"uid":276872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:21:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75e700169d87f844a3a4be67df4159f7141b005e","tid":1913701,"uid":276872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:22:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ef6e9496ba98505e31820788d1e36144b609743",